    "TraditionalChinese": "農作收成"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A strange substance that seems to slowly shift the air around it. It is found in the roots of the <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Gamma Weed plant</span>.<br><br>Gamma Weed requires <span class=\"name name-commodity\">high background radiation</span> to thrive in the wild, but can be farmed in all environments with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hydroponics Tray</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种奇怪的物质，似乎能够缓慢改变四周空气。它生长在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽马草</span>的根部。<br><br>伽马草需要在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高本底辐射</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种奇怪的物质，似乎能够缓慢改变四周空气。它生长在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽马草</span>的根部。<br><br>伽马草需要在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高本底辐射</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境中生存。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種古怪物質，似乎會緩慢改變四周的氣流。可於<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽瑪草植物</span>的根部找到。<br><br>伽瑪草需要<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高背景輻射</span>才能在野外生長，但若借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">水耕盤</span>，便能在任何環境中栽種。"
  },
